{
  "text": "where \u03bb is the wavelength of the light. The estimated band gap of the synthesized BiVO 4 nanoparticles is about 2.8 eV. Note that very few literatures reported the UV-Vis absorption of BiVO 4 nanostructures [CITATION_1] . ",
